casebody.data:
Melchor Zapata DOMINGUEZ, Employee
v.
FRANCISCO DOMINGUEZ MASONRY, INC., Employer, Builders Mutual Insurance Company, Carrier. No. 303P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Dec. 15, 2015. Francisco Bricio, for Dominguez, Melchor Zapata. Jeffrey A. Misenheimer, J. William Crone, IV, Raleigh, for Francisco Dominguez Masonry, Inc., et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 25th of August 2015 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of December 2015."
